	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64265754"><p>A club or a partnership. A pure association doesn't involve having the government protect you from liability for your actions. None of the corporate types would ever accept that they have full liability for their own actions.</p><p>As long as the government is providing liability protection the government has a right, nay, a duty to ensure that they have ways of knowing exactly what's going on inside the corporations.</p></div>
